#: ../../content/applications/services/helpdesk/advanced/track_and_bill.rst:74
msgid ""
"To create a new service product, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> "
"Products --> Products`, and click :guilabel:`New`. This reveals a blank "
"product detail form."
